latestIgtvVideos.title: 3 days Mega Masterclass in Bengaluru
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
3 DAY MEGA MASTER MAKEUP CLASS 

Day 1
>Inauguration by Mr. Pattabhi and Mr. Rajkrish.
>A complete guide to Skin Theory for beginners to Advance .
>Introduction to Color wheel and its applications.
>Difference between Monochromatic and Polychromatic color. 
>A hands-on approach of choosing the right foundation to varies makeup kinds.
>Things to be noted while approaching different skin types and skin tones.
>Fundamentals of selecting the perfect brush for makeup which could bring better results to the makeup. 
>The live approach to the contrast between Natural, Neutral, Glam and Contemporary Makeup.
>A live demo of Natural makeup look just using one Derma palette enhanced through International blending techniques. 
>Hands on experience

Day 2 
>Everything you need to know about the International makeup brands.
>In-depth Knowledge on makeup products.
>The ultimate guide to select product from specific to achieve flawless finish.
>Adoption of current makeup trends. 
>Different types of eye makeup and liner.
>Full Ultra HD makeup look with a 3D eye makeup (High end glam look).
>Hands on practice. 
>Doubts clearance session. 
>Mistakes rectification session. 

Day 3
>Dusky skin/ melanin skin makeup look by using HUDA Beauty, Nars foundation with a Brazilian technique. 
>Airbrush makeup reception look.
>Interactive session. 
>How to book a bride, social media marketing technique. 
>Question and answer session. 
>Certification. 
>Farewell.

TEA BREAK: 11:00am - 11:15am, 03:00pm - 03:15pm  LUNCH BREAK: 01pm - 2pm
( High tea, snacks and lunch will be served)
